1) The ansible version used is 2.4 in Ubuntu 16.04
2) The user creation playbooks with password must have "passlib" installed on the system from were playbook is executed. excute the two command "apt-get install python-pip" and "pip install passlib".once above mentioned commands are executed. you can generate password using "python -c "from passlib.hash import sha512_crypt; import getpass; print sha512_crypt.using(rounds=5000).hash(getpass.getpass())"
" 
  
